{
  "stem": "210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my-- he sold-- he sold the gas station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the first money he got when he poured water into the-- into the gas station where the pumps were down there, so-- and the-- and the-- the gasoline came up.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, they poured water in so the gas would come up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the first gas that they pumped out, this was his first money that he got after the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he sold some property that belonged to his parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he lived in the house that he used to live before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- my cousin came with me, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a, you know, he-- at that time, he already established himself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had like a little soap factory in Opoczno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were, I don't know, maybe 10 people that survived-- some hidden-- most of them hidden-- that survived from Opoczno.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were all-- were like a small little community living together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I got there, you know, there-- there were women that, you know, that didn't-- that didn't have husbands.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a couple that survived with a son.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their name was Frankel; they were hidden-- and a sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of his sisters survived, and she thought that she's gonna marry my husband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when I got there, they didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, they were all-- you know, all jealous and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I got there with my cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was established.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I just didn't like it there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he says, well, if you don't like it here, fine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'll live in Lodz, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and also, a lot of things happened while we were there before we got married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people came back, you now, like from the next town.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
